articles.title: Madonna Announces Rescheduled Dates for North American Leg of Celebration Tour - Hollywood Reporter
articles.description: The tour will officially kick off in London on Oct. 14 and will first visit the U.S. on Dec. 13 at the Barclays Center in Brooklyn.
articles.content:
Madonna, who postponed the July start of her Celebration Tour as she recovered from a bacterial infection, has announced rescheduled dates for her live shows.
The icon’s tour was originally supposed… [+1983 chars]
